---
Syntax: council
        council join
        council <member name>

Manages membership in the Super Council, an in-game governing body available
to players who have been granted the Council flag by an immortal.

  council         -- Lists the current members of the Council.
  council join    -- Adds you to the current Council session. You cannot
                     join if you are already a member.

Access to this command requires the PFLAG_SUPER_COUNCIL player flag. Players
without this flag will receive a "You are not a council member!" message.

Council membership is a role granted by immortals to players involved in
server governance or special events.

See also: politics rulers clan
